remote-studio (9.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian package release for Remote Studio v9.0.
  * Added systemd background daemon.
  * Added multi-monitor TUI support.
  * Applet refactored to use native Settings and Gio.FileMonitor.
  * Tailscale integration for secure auto-sessions.

